Package: dndlights
Title: D&D Spell Sound and Light Effects via LIFX Smart Bulbs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A personal R package for triggering synchronized sound effects
    and LIFX smart light animations on D&D spell casts. Spells are invoked
    as R functions and are designed to be bound to hotkeys or voice commands.
    Requires a LIFX personal access token and a directory of sound effect files.
